4.6. VOLUNTARY SUSPENSION

If the customer wishes, we have the possibility to suspend his line temporarily in ' Voluntary suspension ' in Salesforce.

ATTENTION :

For hey! Internet => A Voluntary Suspension is technically not possible on Internet. From a commercial point of view / churn
risk (for example in case of move or customer is temporarily abroad) you can offer a Voluntary Suspension in the following
way :

- Give an OCC of max 3 months (1 x / year allowed)
- No prolongation possible!
- Line remains active (no suspension in BSCS or Salesforce)

